This paper discusses the design of a search strategy for optimization problems, which is a common topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and operations research (cs.OR). The use of neighborhood structures and local search is also a common technique in optimization, which is related to data structures (cs.DS). The paper also discusses the use of heuristics and algorithmic design, which are topics in machine learning (cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE).
